# 英语四级作文模板范文

---

## 一、议论文模板（正反观点类）⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 【约130词】

### 【挖空模板】

Nowadays, whether **_____(话题)_____** has become a heated topic. Some people believe that it is beneficial, while others hold the opposite view.
（如今，是否_____已成为一个热门话题。一些人认为有益，另一些人持相反观点。）

Those who are in favor of it argue that **_____(好处)_____**. Moreover, it can help people gain valuable experience and broaden their horizons. However, opponents point out that **_____(坏处)_____**. They also worry that it may bring some negative effects.
（支持者认为_____。此外，它可以帮助人们获得宝贵经验、开阔视野。然而，反对者指出_____。他们还担心可能带来一些负面影响。）

From my perspective, I firmly believe that **_____(你的观点)_____**. After all, we should consider this issue from different angles and make a wise decision. Only in this way can we benefit from it.
（在我看来，我坚定地认为_____。毕竟，我们应该从不同角度考虑这个问题，做出明智的决定。只有这样我们才能从中受益。）

#### 好处万能句（直接用）:
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| it can improve students' communication skills | 它能提高学生的沟通能力 |
| it can improve students' language skills | 它能提高学生的语言能力 |
| it can improve students' practical abilities | 它能提高学生的实践能力 |
| it helps people develop good habits of learning | 它帮助人们养成学习的好习惯 |
| it helps people develop good habits of thinking | 它帮助人们养成思考的好习惯 |
| it is beneficial for students' future career | 它对学生未来职业有益 |
| it is beneficial for students' personal growth | 它对学生个人成长有益 |
| it can enrich students' knowledge and broaden their horizons | 它能丰富知识、开阔视野 |
| it plays an important role in personal development | 它在个人发展中起重要作用 |
| it plays an important role in cultivating talents | 它在培养人才中起重要作用 |

#### 坏处万能句（直接用）:
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| it may take up too much time and energy | 它可能占用太多时间和精力 |
| it may distract students from their major studies | 它可能分散学生对专业学习的注意力 |
| it may add extra burden to students | 它可能给学生增加额外负担 |
| it may reduce students' interest in learning | 它可能降低学生的学习兴趣 |
| not everyone is interested in it | 不是每个人都对它感兴趣 |
| it may have some negative effects on students' health | 它可能对学生健康产生负面影响 |
| it may have some negative effects on academic performance | 它可能对学业成绩产生负面影响 |

#### 我的观点万能句（直接用）:
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| I strongly support this idea because it benefits students | 我强烈支持这个想法，因为它对学生有益 |
| I strongly support this idea because the advantages outweigh the disadvantages | 我强烈支持，因为利大于弊 |
| it is necessary for students' all-round development | 它对学生全面发展是必要的 |
| it is essential for cultivating well-rounded talents | 它对培养全面人才至关重要 |
| the advantages outweigh the disadvantages | 利大于弊 |
| we should find a balance between study and practice | 我们应该在学习和实践之间找到平衡 |
| we should find a balance between work and rest | 我们应该在工作和休息之间找到平衡 |
| this practice should be encouraged and promoted | 这种做法应该被鼓励和推广 |

### 【范文】大学语文是否应成为必修课（约135词）

Nowadays, whether _主题_ has become a heated topic. Some people believe that it is beneficial, while others hold the opposite view.
（如今，_主题_已成为一个热门话题。一些人认为有益，另一些人持相反观点。）

Those who are in favor of it argue that it can improve students' "language skills" and enrich their cultural knowledge. 
Moreover, it can help people gain valuable experience and broaden their horizons. 
However, opponents point out that it may "add extra burden to students who already have heavy coursework". 
They also worry that it may bring some negative effects.
（支持者认为它能提高学生的语言能力并丰富他们的文化知识。此外，它可以帮助人们获得宝贵经验、开阔视野。然而，反对者指出它可能给课业繁重的学生增加额外负担。他们还担心可能带来一些负面影响。）

From my perspective, I firmly believe that "College Chinese should be a compulsory" course 
because it is essential for cultivating well-rounded talents. 
After all, we should consider this issue from different angles and make a wise decision. Only in this way can we benefit from it.
（在我看来，我坚信大学语文应该是必修课，因为它对培养全面发展的人才至关重要。毕竟，我们应该从不同角度考虑这个问题，做出明智的决定。只有这样我们才能从中受益。）

---

**【填空对照】**
| 空位 | 填入内容 |
|------|----------|
| 话题 | making College Chinese a compulsory course |
| 好处 | it can improve students' language skills and enrich their cultural knowledge |
| 坏处 | it may add extra burden to students who already have heavy coursework |
| 观点 | College Chinese should be a compulsory course because it is essential for cultivating well-rounded talents |
Those who are in favor of it argue that 

### 【套用示例】大学生兼职（约130词）

Nowadays, whether **college students should take part-time jobs** has become a heated topic. Some people believe that it is beneficial, while others hold the opposite view.

Those who are in favor of it argue that **students can gain work experience and reduce family financial burden**. Moreover, it can help people gain valuable experience and broaden their horizons. However, opponents point out that **it may distract students from studies**. They also worry that it may bring some negative effects.

From my perspective, I firmly believe that **students should take part-time jobs as long as they balance work and study**. After all, we should consider this issue from different angles and make a wise decision. Only in this way can we benefit from it.

---

## 二、问题解决型模板 ⭐⭐⭐ 【约120词】

### 【挖空模板】

In modern society, **_____(问题)_____** has become an increasingly common problem among people. It is essential for us to find effective ways to cope with it.
（在现代社会，_____已成为人们越来越普遍的问题。我们必须找到有效的方法来应对。）

There are several reasons for this problem. First, **_____(原因)_____**. Second, many people lack awareness of this issue. To solve it, we can take the following measures: **_____(措施)_____**. Besides, we should develop good habits in our daily life.
（这个问题有几个原因。首先，_____。其次，很多人缺乏对这个问题的认识。为了解决它，我们可以采取以下措施：_____。此外，我们应该在日常生活中养成良好的习惯。）

In conclusion, although this problem is challenging, we can manage it effectively by adopting a positive attitude. Only in this way can we live a happier and healthier life.
（总之，虽然这个问题很有挑战性，但我们可以通过采取积极的态度来有效管理。只有这样，我们才能过上更幸福、更健康的生活。）

### 【套用示例】如何应对压力（约125词）

In modern society, **stress** has become an increasingly common problem among people. It is essential for us to find effective ways to cope with it.

There are several reasons for this problem. First, **the fast pace of life and fierce competition put great pressure on us**. Second, many people lack awareness of this issue. To solve it, we can take the following measures: **maintaining a healthy lifestyle and communicating with friends**. Besides, we should develop good habits in our daily life.

In conclusion, although this problem is challenging, we can manage it effectively by adopting a positive attitude. Only in this way can we live a happier and healthier life.

---

## 三、书信类模板 ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 【约120词】

### 【通用书信模板】（填3处）

Dear Sir or Madam,

I am writing to **_____(目的：apply for申请/suggest建议/invite邀请)_____**. I hope you could take a few minutes to read my letter.
（我写信是为了_____。希望您能花几分钟阅读我的信。）

First of all, **_____(内容1)_____**. Besides, **_____(内容2)_____**. Moreover, I have a strong sense of responsibility and I am confident that I can handle it well.
（首先，_____。此外，_____。而且，我有强烈的责任感，我有信心能做好。）

I would appreciate it if you could consider my request. Thank you for your time and attention. I am looking forward to your favorable reply at your earliest convenience.
（如果您能考虑我的请求，我将不胜感激。感谢您的时间和关注。期待您尽早回复。）

Yours sincerely,
Li Ming

---

### 【书信万能填空句】

#### 写信目的（直接用）：
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| offer some suggestions on how to improve the service | 就如何改进服务提一些建议 |
| invite you to attend our graduation ceremony | 邀请您参加我们的毕业典礼 |
| invite you to give a lecture on English learning | 邀请您做一个关于英语学习的讲座 |
| apply for the position of volunteer | 申请志愿者职位 |
| express my gratitude for your help | 表达对您帮助的感谢 |
| ask for your advice on how to learn English well | 请教您如何学好英语 |

#### 建议内容（直接用）：
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| make a detailed plan and stick to it | 制定详细计划并坚持执行 |
| practice speaking English every day | 每天练习说英语 |
| read more books to broaden your horizons | 多读书以开阔视野 |
| take part in more social activities | 多参加社交活动 |
| maintain a positive attitude towards life | 保持积极的生活态度 |
| balance your study and rest properly | 合理平衡学习和休息 |

#### 活动内容（直接用）：
| 模板句 | 中文 |
|--------|------|
| there will be various performances and games | 将有各种表演和游戏 |
| we will have a speech contest and a talent show | 我们将举办演讲比赛和才艺表演 |
| students will share their learning experiences | 学生们将分享他们的学习经验 |
| experts will give lectures on career planning | 专家将做职业规划讲座 |
| we will visit the museum and have a discussion | 我们将参观博物馆并进行讨论 |

---

### 【建议信】⭐高频（填2处）【约120词】

Dear _____,

I am writing to offer some practical suggestions on **_____(话题)_____**. I have learned about your situation and I hope my advice will be of some help to you.
（我写信是想就_____提一些实用建议。我了解到您的情况，希望我的建议对您有所帮助。）

First and foremost, I strongly suggest that you should **_____(建议内容)_____**. In addition, it would be a good idea to seek advice from experienced people around you. Last but not least, please remember that practice makes perfect and patience is the key to success.
（首先，我强烈建议你应该_____。此外，向你身边有经验的人寻求建议是个好主意。最后，请记住熟能生巧，耐心是成功的关键。）

I sincerely hope you will find these suggestions helpful and practical. Please feel free to contact me if you have any further questions. I wish you all the best and I am looking forward to your good news.
（我真诚地希望这些建议对您有帮助且实用。如有任何问题请随时联系我。祝您一切顺利，期待您的好消息。）

Yours sincerely,
Li Ming

---

### 【邀请信】⭐高频（填2处）【约120词】

Dear _____,

I am writing to invite you to **_____(活动)_____** which will be held next week at our school. It would be a great honor to have you there.
（我写信邀请您参加_____，活动将于下周在我校举行。您的到来将是我们的荣幸。）

During the event, **_____(活动内容)_____**. I believe it will be a wonderful opportunity for all of us to learn and communicate with each other.
（活动期间，_____。我相信这对我们所有人来说都是一个学习和交流的好机会。）

I would be greatly honored if you could come. Please let me know your decision at your earliest convenience. I am looking forward to your reply.
（如果您能来，我将深感荣幸。请尽早告知您的决定。期待您的回复。）

Yours sincerely,
Li Ming

---
